com.ojcoleman.ahni.integration

Class ParamCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ojcoleman.ahni.integration.ParamCollection

  • public class ParamCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of ParamGenes or sub-ParamCollections. A ParamGene will have an index within its ParamCollection, and if a ParamCollection has a super-ParamCollection it will have in index within it. The main function of a ParamCollection is to define common properties of ParamGenes or collections thereof. Note that a ParamCollection does not maintain references to its sub-collections or genes.
